name: 5D
description:
The face of purity, calm, nothing and everything.
5 Dimensions, because this represents the absolute climax, a state that can only be accessed through love and detaching yourself from self-representation with the self (the ego).
It is easy to represent it, but it hurts, because you leave behind many patterns that we have pre-established.
Break your karma, connect with your being, transcend into 5D.

28 Second Loop 
60 FPS
2150 x 1975 px
Music made by me in an altered state of consciousness.
